# Deploy workflow

When the user asks to deploy (or ship/publish changes to production):

1. Commit all relevant project changes with a clear message (unless there is nothing to commit).
2. Push to `origin` on the current branch (`master` / tracking branch).
3. Deploy to Vercel production (`npx vercel deploy --prod --yes`).

Do not leave working-tree changes only on Vercel — GitHub should stay in sync after every deploy.
